    i.cube.icon 
    | Example
    
include ./hacknbreak.pug

//-
    Match with Design Guide status:

        [x] 1. Example implementation
        [x] 2. Simple variable
        [x] 3. Unbound instances
        [x] 4. Bound instances and/or live feed
        [x] 5. {{#if }} ... {{/if}} block
        [x] 6. Test on mobile
